med from that account is **delegation**, thanks to an existing authorization granted to the [Delegation SubDAO](https://daodao.zone/dao/juno1ehayefjmlty0zvqdjs2l7tkamtgq3jpuucrjjs568lhapxjcd3xs6rf8ma/home).\n\nFull text [here](https://github.com/CosmosContracts/roadmap/blob/main/proposals/99-extra-delegation-program.md)","proposer":"juno1s33zct2zhhaf60x4a90cpe9yquw99jj0zen8pt","expedited":false,"failed_reason":""}}
